import React from 'react';
import { Avatar, Box, Container, Grid, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import Navbar from './components/Navbar';
import AccountCard from './components/AccountCard';
import AddAccount from './components/AddAccount';
import { Component } from 'react';

class Home extends Component {
    render() {
        return(
            <Box>
                <Navbar/>
                <Container sx={{mt: 4, mb: 4}}>
                    <Grid container justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" spacing={3}>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Amazon"
                        firstChar="A"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitter"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Google"
                        firstChar="G"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Linkedn"
                        firstChar="L"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitch"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitch"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitch"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitch"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitch"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                        <AccountCard 
                        title="Twitch"
                        firstChar="T"/>
                    </Grid>
                    <AddAccount/>     
                </Container>
                
            </Box>
        );
    }
}

export default Home;
